-- Auchan to Open Two Stores a Year in Ukraine, Kommersant Reports
-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 2012-10-24T06:32:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-24/auchan-to-open-two-stores-a-year-in-ukraine-kommersant-reports.html
French Groupe Auchan SA plans to
open two hypermarkets in Ukraine a year from 2014,  Kommersant-
Ukraine  reported, citing Gerard Gallet, director of Auchan
operations in Ukraine.  Auchan will invest an average 20 million euro ($26 million)
in each new hypermarket, the newspaper said, citing Gallet.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
 kchoursina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
